{"article_id":"vdumvJXK7lUUwCsP","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Mitt Romney said on Wednesday","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"that the individual mandate in President Obama ' s health care law was \" a tax , \"","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"just days after his campaign said","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"the candidate had rejected that characterization .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"In an interview with Jan Crawford of CBS News , Mr. Romney said :","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"\" While I agreed with the dissent ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"that ' s taken over by the fact","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"that the majority of the court said","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"it ' s a tax ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"and therefore it is a tax .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"They have spoken . \"","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"\" They concluded","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"it was a tax .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"That ' s what it is ,","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"and the American people know","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"that President Obama has broken the pledge","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"he made , \"","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"he added .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"\" He said","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"he wouldn ' t raise taxes on middle-income Americans .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"Not only did he raise the $ 500 billion","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"that was already in the bill ,","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"it ' s now clear that his mandate","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"as described by the Supreme Court","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"is a tax . \"","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"On Monday , Mr. Romney ' s presidential campaign said","depth":4},{"id":26,"text":"that the health care mandate should be thought of as a penalty and not as a tax .","depth":4},{"id":27,"text":"That statement , by the campaign ' s spokesman , Eric Fehrnstrom , was at odds from the general line of leading Republicans in Congress and elsewhere ,","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"who have spent the last several days","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"eagerly accusing the president of levying a new tax .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"\" The governor disagreed with the ruling of the court , \"","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"Mr. Fehrnstrom said Monday on MSNBC ' s \" The Daily Rundown. \"","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"\" He agreed with the dissent","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"written by Justice Scalia ,","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"which very clearly stated","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"that the mandate was not a tax . \"","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"The issue","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"of how to characterize the mandate","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"is a sensitive one for the Romney campaign ,","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"given how Mr. Romney championed universal health care in Massachusetts","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"when he was governor there .","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"While Mr. Romney has pledged to repeal what conservatives call Obamacare ,","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"he had previously largely avoided calling the mandate a tax ,","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"perhaps because his Massachusetts plan included a similar mandate .","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"Mr. Romney made his comment","depth":4},{"id":45,"text":"while vacationing Wednesday in New Hampshire .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":91,"left":70,"right":90,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":49,"right":69,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":49,"left":47,"right":48,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":47,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":48,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":69,"left":55,"right":68,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":55,"left":4,"right":54,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":54,"left":53,"right":10,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":53,"left":5,"right":52,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":52,"left":6,"ri